### Health Check - Local
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Health Check - Render
GET https://cooking-merrilly.onrender.com

### Get all recipes
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes

### Get recipe by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/{}

### Create a recipe
POST http://localhost:3000/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Recipe",
  "ingredients": [
    { "text": "1 cup flour" },
    { "text": "2 eggs", "optional": true }
  ],
  "steps": [
    "Mix ingredients",
    "Bake at 350F for 20 minutes"
  ],
  "tags": ["test", "baking"]
}

### Update a recipe
PUT http://localhost:3000/recipes/{}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Recipe Title"
}

### Delete a recipe
DELETE http://localhost:3000/recipes/{}